body{
  font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
}

.product-card__name {
  letter-spacing: normal;
}

.prices__value {
  font-weight: bold;
}

.header__search {
  border: solid 2px;
  border-radius: 6px;
}

.header__search-btn {
  font-size: 17px;
  color: #000000;
  margin-bottom: -17px;
}

.header__nav {
    padding-top: 15px;
}

.header__buttons .btn .badge {
    border-radius: 3px;
}

.top-bar a.top-bar__countdown {
    color: #000000;
}

.header__nav--full a {
    color: #333;
}

.menu__item {
    color: #333;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}
